{"tid":414837,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰台北新飛機餐 4 款熱餐任君選擇","createTime":"2017-09-26T13:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T11:53:22.000Z","uid":28366,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5bf6640bbca45751f7d3960bd5e3cee0e11ad3e4","tid":414837,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/gotripfeatureimage2_115481722559ca26464086b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fgotripfeatureimage2_115481722559ca26464086b.jpg&h=1afdf8c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以往國泰航空飛台北航線的飛機餐只會奉上一個雞捲，份量少之餘味道亦乏善可陳，因此受到不少旅客批評。而國泰最近聽取了乘客的意見，決定由10月1日起，於該航線輪流提供4款迎合港人口味的主食，包括焗豬扒飯、粟米魚塊配蛋炒飯、叉燒飯和葡汁雞飯，滿足乘客的口腹之慾。編者近日就前往國泰空廚中心觀看飛機餐製作流程，還率先試食了4款新飛機餐，即睇評價如何！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">台北飛機餐 雞捲變熱餐</span><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空飛台北航班供應的雞捲，除了味道不太討好之外，每次空姐派餐前都要摺紙袋、綁絲帶，加上翻熱的時間，空姐們其實十分忙碌。而且所有紙袋即用即棄，超唔環保！所以國泰最近終於推出4款熱餐，取代雞捲。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_4897_51461783159ca1ee062518-807x538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_4897_51461783159ca1ee062518-807x538.jpg&h=32969f1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_4934_123813397459ca1ed7a6484-807x538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_4934_123813397459ca1ed7a6484-807x538.jpg&h=97122ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">4款主食輪流供應！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_4899_134243710859ca1edeb8e30-807x538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_4899_134243710859ca1edeb8e30-807x538.jpg&h=c18f78b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">用錫紙兜上，一開蓋有煙出，夠熱！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">焗豬扒飯</span><br />\n</span><br />\n焗豬扒飯頗足料，有3塊豬扒，亦有不少蘑菇、蕃茄等配料。蕃茄醬味道濃郁，醬汁的份量亦夠「撈飯」，整體來說不會太乾身，與市面上快餐店的豬扒飯味道相似。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_4913_32353907459ca1edd1f33f-807x538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_4913_32353907459ca1edd1f33f-807x538.jpg&h=54081f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以飛機餐嚟講，豬扒都算大塊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">粟米魚塊配蛋炒飯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n味道同香港人平時吃的粟米斑腩飯如出一轍，但飛機餐中的魚塊味道較淡，肉質亦偏䭃身、易碎。不過粟米粒及醬汁都夠鮮甜，蛋炒飯質素不俗。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_4893_151611291259ca1ee292d75-538x807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_4893_151611291259ca1ee292d75-538x807.jpg&h=07a9dfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">整體味道較淡，上到飛機食可能會覺得更清淡！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_1828_160449794859ca1f1275918-807x605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_1828_160449794859ca1f1275918-807x605.jpg&h=9aa01e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">夠多汁唔會乾身！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">叉燒飯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n燒味飯是香港最有代表性的食物之一，在飛機上食又是另一番風味。編者試食的叉燒飯中，叉燒肥瘦適中，肉質較軟不會太韌，加上燒味飯必備的甜豉油，味道不錯。惟每盒只得一條菜心，少之餘菜心亦較老，難以咬斷。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_1829_180514819459ca1f105470a-807x605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_1829_180514819459ca1f105470a-807x605.jpg&h=f79051ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">叉燒肥瘦適中，味道不錯。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">葡汁雞飯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n葡汁份量多，帶有椰香味，「撈飯」一流！盒中有3-4件雞件，肉質嫩滑，亦有薯仔等配菜，材料豐富。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_1830-1_74517137259ca1f0e87ef0-807x605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_1830-1_74517137259ca1f0e87ef0-807x605.jpg&h=c8099270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">葡汁椰香味濃，撈飯一流！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">台北回程亦有變化</span><br />\n<br />\n而由台北回程的航線亦會送上富當地特色的飛機餐，如魯肉飯、炒米粉等。不過回程飛機餐由台灣相關機構製造，記者今次未有機會一嚐台灣提供的餐點，希望日後飛台北的讀者可以一試！<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/bl_t2_49554480959ca1f1823e74-807x539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fbl_t2_49554480959ca1f1823e74-807x539.jpg&h=d432e328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聽聞台北回程會有魯肉飯供應！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">10月1開始 試行3個月！</span><br />\n<br />\n先導計劃會由10月1日開始，預計推行3個月，每半個月更換飛機餐款式，輪流供應4款主食。收集客人意見之後，會考慮長期供應幾款飛機餐或推廣至其他航線，所以有份試食的乘客記得向國泰反映意見！<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/img_4939_104225698959ca1ed619cbe-807x538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fimg_4939_104225698959ca1ed619cbe-807x538.jpg&h=b4e4fdc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">之後有份試食嘅乘客記得向航空公司反映意見！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">飛台北的其他飛機餐</span><br />\n<br />\n飛台北的航空公司總共有 4 間，除了以上提及的國泰航空之外，還有香港航空、中華航空及長榮航空，港航同華航就長期都貨應熱餐，而長榮最近都轉為供應蛋糕，現在轉型的國泰就不是排包尾了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/-2017-09-26-4.56.05_17921510359ca16cfa2f69-1024x595.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F-2017-09-26-4.56.05_17921510359ca16cfa2f69-1024x595.png&h=45673d2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">華航也是由 16 年年尾開始重新提供熱餐。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/-2017-09-26-4.56.16_77862332259ca16f12a8a2-1024x595.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F-2017-09-26-4.56.16_77862332259ca16f12a8a2-1024x595.png&h=ea4b4000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">而且華航一共有 5 款熱餐，而國泰暫時就只有 4 款。</span>"},{"pid":"1d1b3fe6ae83a60df90b71061c9e06c47ce57df2","tid":414837,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a2a82a8578bc388bd7e42329b071ec1c5d7205","tid":414837,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"啲廚師戴咁高頂帽<br />\n但啲野仲係咁難食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d54e579311e0a4ab6aae611ab277c0415b7172","tid":414837,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"波仔飯"},{"pid":"c79339df8671a39517a07cdf69251fe1572e4aee","tid":414837,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf11a90ded9a447d16b22c3da8bd2905c813806","tid":414837,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"未熟叉燒<br />\n仲有香港特色嘔吐物飯"},{"pid":"63e02d250f4d3feaecfdd8bf6192b5485d1e66f5","tid":414837,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T22:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915a1668746e51b3c4809010d317210899b353a9","tid":414837,"uid":130247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f732b59b6aa54935bc857a072eb44c12961404","tid":414837,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"想問下而家仲有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係又派返卷"}]}